<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VaultShare - Settings</title>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #F8C471; }
        .container-settings {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }
        .settings-section {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .btn-purple {
            background-color: #6C3483;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-purple:hover { background-color: #5B2C6F; }
        .profile-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .profile-img-placeholder img{
            background-color: #E0E0E0;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
        }
        .input-field {
            background-color: #EFEFEF;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .toggle-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .update-payment-method .form-control {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .btn-outline {
            border: 1px solid #6C3483;
            color: #6C3483;
        }
        .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: #6C3483;
            color: white;
        }
        .toggle-password {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .input-group {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px; 
        }
        .custom-input {
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            width: 100%; 
            flex: 1; 
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        .custom-btn {
            background-color: #6C3483; 
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            margin-right: 5px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .custom-btn:hover {
            background-color: #5A2D71;
        }
        .button-group {
            display: flex;
        }

        .form-control-change1 {
            width: 150px;
            display: block; 
            padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem; 
            font-size: 1rem; 
            line-height: 1.5; 
            color: #495057; 
            background-color: #fff; 
            background-clip: padding-box; 
            border: 1px solid #ced4da; 
            border-radius: 0.25rem; 
            transition: border-color .15s ease-in-out, box-shadow .15s ease-in-out; 
        }
        .form-control-change2{
            width: 150px;
            position: relative;
            left: 10px;
            display: block; 
            padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem; 
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5; 
            color: #495057; 
            background-color: #fff;
            background-clip: padding-box; 
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
            border-radius: 0.25rem; 
            transition: border-color .15s ease-in-out, box-shadow .15s ease-in-out; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-settings">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="profile-card">
                    <div class="profile-img-placeholder">
                        <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/049/209/831/small_2x/young-woman-smiling-with-natural-beauty-against-a-plain-background-in-a-bright-and-cheerful-setting-png.png" alt="User Avatar">
                    </div>
                    <h5>#janedoe</h5>
                    <p>$1500</p>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="input-field">
                    <span>Change Username</span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control-change1" placeholder="Input">
                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">&times;</button>
                </div>
                <div class="input-field">
                    <span>Change Bio</span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control-change2" placeholder="Input">
                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">&times;</button>
                </div>
            </div>




            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="settings-section">
                    <h5>Push Notifications</h5>
                    <p>Would you like to enable or disable push notifications?</p>
                    <div class="toggle-buttons">
                        <button class="custom-btn">Enable</button>
                        <button class="custom-btn">Disable</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="settings-section update-payment-method">
                    <h5>Update Payment Method</h5>
                    <p>Update your card details.</p>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Name on card">
                    <div class="d-flex">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control mr-2" placeholder="Expiry">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="CVV">
                    </div>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Card number">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mt-3">
                        <button class="custom-btn">Cancel</button>
                        <button class="custom-btn">Update</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="settings-section">
                    <h5>Reset Password</h5>
                    <p>Choose a new password for your account</p>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="password" class="custom-input" placeholder="Your new password">
                        <span class="toggle-password">&#128065;</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="password" class="custom-input" placeholder="Confirm your new password">
                        <span class="toggle-password">&#128065;</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="button-group">
                        <button class="custom-btn">Reset Password</button>
                        <button class="custom-btn custom-btn-outline">Sign Out</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>




        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
